                     <interp inst="t18800628-429-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18800628-429-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bankrupcy"></interp>, Unlawfully omitting to disclose to their trustee in bankruptcy goods to the value of 8,000<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. and 1,330<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. and other sums; also to obtaining goods on credit within four months of their bankruptcy.</rs>
